{"tid":1949618,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衞（WHO) 反對「封關」：會打擊旅遊業","createTime":"2020-03-29T18:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T19:42:50.000Z","uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"09959332ff0036ee3511f52aa601f4f78485bb6d","tid":1949618,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:45:48.000Z","msg":"世衞區域負責人克盧格（Hans Kluge）表示，意大利受疫情的影響最為嚴重，最近個案數量急增，部分病人沒有明確的感染路徑，為政府帶來極大挑戰。他指意大利政府將公眾健康置於經濟繁榮之上，是艱難但正確的決定。他強調，疫情所造成的負擔最終會由各國一起承擔，因此各國無論目前是否有個案，也應合作防疫。意大利衞生部長斯佩蘭扎稱，不建議暫停履行神根公約，指各國都同意開放邊境，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">封關既無效，也不恰當</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n  歐盟要求成員國評估他們應對疫情的計劃，並上報歐盟。歐盟疾控中心認為，歐洲其他國家也可能出現類似意大利的情形，但仍有信心阻止疫情進一步擴散。聯合國世界旅遊組織及世衞周三發表聯合聲明，指根據目前形勢，世衞不建議各國實施任何旅行或貿易限制。聲明提及，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過度限制旅行會對國際交通造成不必要的干擾，對旅遊業造成負面影響</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"4b0eb6782b95378b4c1aafc2d4d433a21222d434","tid":1949618,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:46:11.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200227/mobile/bkn-20200227123010675-0227_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200227%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200227123010675-0227_00912_001.html&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq4%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=26d73889\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200227/mobile/bkn-20200227123010675-0227_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d320d564cfd46c43a899cdccc63639672b08ea58","tid":1949618,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:49:21.000Z","msg":"無啦啦講埋經濟？"},{"pid":"f1276710d4e9ad02fb5c946d0603d35e7ad0d331","tid":1949618,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:51:06.000Z","msg":"旅遊業關你世衛咩事？"},{"pid":"e03b90f431a1068cf76a7f376e82d93cea6236b3","tid":1949618,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:51:22.000Z","msg":"其實世界衛生組織點解要講影響經濟？關佢乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2b3bd155de64397d54ca4ea5f6aec4c1954042","tid":1949618,"uid":131025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那都好似封左關喎"},{"pid":"c67b9f4981ca50bb2176afd720552c4f21654e5b","tid":1949618,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:56:00.000Z","msg":"就算唔封關旅遊業都收緊皮"},{"pid":"a3d6870f1881e17aff300dfc4b22faa6ee3a115a","tid":1949618,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T19:42:50.000Z","msg":"Old news <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}